    "summary": "\u201cRisk is the only certainty in your life, how do you cope with it?\u201d  \n\nThe European financial services sector is my domain, but I also support big, complex companies in other sectors. I advise their senior and C-level management on their Risk management, Compliance and Governance. These solutions enable organizations to optimize their governance structure and governance alignment, handle risks effectively and cost-efficiently, and integrate compliance into their processes, smart   and flexible.\n\n I have been working  as a risk consultant in more than 26 countries at several large financial organizations. My specialty is Governance, Risk management and Compliance.  I have considerable experience with the Basel II regulations, financial regulations in order to increase the control of the financial organizations. I take pride in the fact that a number of big international companies are today using the Risk management and Compliance method I implemented there. Key in those projects were convincing clear communication and connection of different cultures. I am a cooperative person and critical in a positive way and I like to share my experience by writing articles and giving lectures on Risk management. \nSpecialties: \nChange management \nProcess Re-engineering \nProgram / Project Management Problem Solution,  \nClient engagement, \nWorking in collaboration with others, \nRisk Identification \nRisk & Control Framework Investigations/implementations,",
